02. Welcome Message

Input:

Ouput:

Explanation:

Sample Input 1:

Preethi

Sample Output 1:

Welcome Preethi

Sample Input 2:

Naresh Kumar

Sample Output 2:

Welcome Naresh Kumar

Solution:

def say_wishes(arg_1):
    wishes = "Welcome " + arg_1
    print(wishes)

name = input()
say_wishes(name)

