04. Divisible by Seven - 2

Input:

Ouput:

Explanation:

Sample Input 1:

14

Sample Output 1:

True

Sample Input 2:

15

Sample Output 2:

False

Solution:

def divisible_by_seven(arg_1):
    remainder = arg_1 % 7
    if remainder == 0:
        result = True
    else:
        result = False
    print(result)
    
n = int(input())
divisible_by_seven(n)

